api_overview.title: API Overview
api_overview.general_information: This API provides programmatic access to manage resources. All requests and responses are handled in JSON format. Rate limits are applied per IP address and authenticated user.

authentication_authorization.title: Authentication & Authorization
authentication_authorization.authentication_process: Authentication is performed using a JSON Web Token (JWT) obtained after successful login (not documented here).
authentication_authorization.token_format: The token is a standard JWT string.
authentication_authorization.authorization_levels: Access to specific endpoints is determined by the scope embedded within the JWT (e.g., 'admin', 'read:users', 'write:users').
